  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Health and Family Welfare`)
  (str department) (str `Department of Health and Family Welfare`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to control the advertisement of drugs in certain cases, to prohibit the advertisement for certain purposes of remedies alleged to possess magic qualities and to provide for matters connected therewith.`)
